These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, architect, journalist
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, marigold, azalea
1. the person who growsbellflower is not to the left of the person who growsazalea##8
2. the journalist is somewhere to the right of the person who growsazalea##5
3. the person who growsazalea is between the architect and the journalist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |     3      |
| Job         | architect | analyst   | journalist |
| Flower   | marigold | azalea | bellflower        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, tea
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, satire, thriller
1. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person watching adventure movies##7
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
3. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | tea | cola   | soy-milk   |
| Movie-Genre        | satire | thriller | adventure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-3::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, nectarine, strawberry
3 different games are played: whist, monopoly, backgammon
1. the person eating cauliflower is not to the left of the person playing monopoly##8
2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere between the person eating cauliflower and the person playing whist##7
3. the person eating strawberry is not to the left of the person playing backgammon##8
4. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |
| Food        | nectarine | strawberry | cauliflower |
| Game   | whist       | backgammon     | monopoly         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, architect, bartender
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, reggae, ambient
1. the bartender is not to the right of the architect##8
2. the bartender is on the right of the analyst##1
3. the fan of rock is somewhere between the fan of reggae and the analyst##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job           | analyst | bartender | architect |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | rock | reggae    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-5::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, musician, accountant
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse, turtle
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the accountant is on the left or right of the musician##3
3. the accountant is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5
4. the musician is not to the right of the police-officer##8
5. the owner of the horse is on the left of the accountant##1
6. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |
| Job   | musician | accountant | police-officer |
| Pet           | horse    | turtle      | hedgehog  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-6::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, cycling, snowboarding
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, horse
1. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##5
2. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##5
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |   2    |       3        |
| Sport   | cycling | rowing | snowboarding |
| Pet   | horse        | goat   | chinchilla     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-7::.
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, italian, russian
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, pilot, writer
1. the pilot is between the writer and the russian##2
2. the italian is not to the left of the writer##8
3. the russian is not to the left of the writer##8
4. the writer is the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |
| Nationality   | japanese | italian | russian |
| Job        | writer      | pilot    | lawyer |

