3. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the right of the person eating peas##5
4. the person eating lemon is not to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |
| Food   | spinach | peas    | lemon |
| Sport         | skiing  | climbing | swimming |

