.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, snowboarding, rowing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, drama, romance
1. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
2. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
3. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Sport          | rowing | cycling  | snowboarding |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | drama | romance   |

