.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-10::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, dancing, skydiving
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, tennis, weightlifting
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
5. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |       2       |    3     |
| Hobby   | dancing | skydiving        | singing    |
| Sport      | tennis  | weightlifting | biathlon |

