.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-11::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, mango, peach
City: hannover, nizza, boston
1. the person eating peach is not to the left of the person traveling to hannover##8
2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |   2   |     3     |
| Food   | mango    | peach | asparagus |
| City    | nizza | hannover   | boston     |

