2. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
3. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | fanta | soy-milk | hot-chocolate    |
| Transport     | train  | trike   | quad-bike |

