.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-14::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, sprite
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, game, prince
1. the person drinking juice is the prince-smoker##1
2. the game-smoker is somewhere between the prince-smoker and the person drinking iced-tea##7
3. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | juice     | sprite | iced-tea   |
| Cigar      | prince | game | ritmeester |

