.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-17::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, electronic, house
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, brown, emerald
1. the fan of house is not to the right of the person who likes brown##8
2. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the fan of house##1
3. the fan of house is between the fan of electronic and the fan of d&b##2
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
5. the fan of electronic is not to the left of the person who likes brown##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b       | house      | electronic |
| Color         | green | brown | emerald     |

