2. the american is not to the left of the owner of the snake##8
3. the american is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |      3      |
| Pet         | mouse | snake | turtle |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | brazilian    | american    |

 